421
00:22:45,360 --> 00:22:48,440
You killed Yang Zhiyuan and his family.

422
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:50,040
I can ignore it, too.

423
00:22:50,840 --> 00:22:53,720
But you conspired with Lei Jing

424
00:22:53,720 --> 00:22:55,280
for my son's life.

425
00:22:56,160 --> 00:22:56,840
Your son…

426
