434
00:23:21,680 --> 00:23:22,760
I beg you, my lord.

435
00:23:22,920 --> 00:23:24,440
Please spare my life.

436
00:23:24,680 --> 00:23:25,320
I…

437
00:23:25,800 --> 00:23:27,880
